---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer, trunc(_score, 3) as _score FROM vector_search(qs_view, 'secondary') where subject!='math' order by _score desc, id LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                      |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: _score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary")).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                       |
|               |   Projection: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary")).id, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary")).answer, trunc(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary"))._score, Int64(3)) AS _score |
|               |     TableScan: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary")) projection=[_score, answer, id], full_filters=[vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary")).subject != Utf8("math")]                |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [_score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=4                                                                                                                    |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[_score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                        |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@1 AS Int64) as id, answer@0 as answer, trunc(1 - distance@2, 3) as _score]                                                                             |
|               |       CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |         RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                              |
|               |           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |             CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |               S3VectorsQueryExec (INDEX_NAME_1): filter={subject:{$ne:"math"}} limit=100                                                                                                  |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                           |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
